init:
    image bg blackscreen = "blackscreen.jpg"
    image bg worklaptop = "worklaptop.jpg"

label Day_4_start:

    scene bg blackscreen
    play music "StressfulAmbiance.mp3" loop

    "(Did I miss work? How many days have passed? where am I?)"

    "(I did not bother to check my clock I immediately went to the bathroom and looked at myself in the mirror.)"

    "(Am I a few inches shorter? What is happening?)"

    fly "..."

    "(It feels like static is eating at my brain.)"

    "(But.)"

    "(I.)"

    "(Have.)"

    "(To.)"

    "(Go.)"

    "(To.)"

    jump Day_4_office


label Day_4_office:


    boss "Fly do not multitask during standup."

    fly "..."

    boss "You should be paying attention to everything that is said. You need to understand what your other coworkers are doing, if one of them is out, we'll need you to step up alright?"

    fly "..."

    boss "I don't want to have this conversation again, get to it alright, Thank you."

    fly "..."

    "(Work. Yes I have some work to do, let me check my tickets again.)"

    "(I began reading the tickets, as I was reading I found myself in a state of tortured repetition.)"

    "'As a developer I-'"
    "'As a developer-'"
    "'As-'"
    "'As a developer I will ana-'"
    "'As a developer I will analyze'"
    "'As a-'"

    "(I can't read this. It was like everytime I attempted to progress an electric shock would restart my ability to think.)"

    "(I needed to take a walk, get a drink, something.)"

    "(As I got up I suddenly got a call from Bodhi, I accepted the call.)"

    jump Day_4_Consecutive_Calls

label Day_4_Consecutive_Calls:

    scene bg worklaptop

    lead "Hello, good morning. How far were you able to get on the documentation I asked you to complete."

    fly "..."

    "(I had a documentation task? I did not see a ticket for it.)"

    lead "Did you already forget? This is very frustrating, I told you during standup. Please complete it and get back to me."

    "(The call ended, I had no idea what I had to document.)"

    "(I decided to get up again to get some water but another call intercepted me.)"

    "(It was from Drucker, I accepted it.)"

    boss "Hello Hello, just wanted to know if you read the ticket I just created for you so we can go over it if you have any questions."

    "(There is another ticket assigned to me?)"

    boss "Ok you have not read it obviously, please read it and don't waste our time, thank you."

    "(I again attempted to get up, only for Bodhi to call me again, I ignored the call this time to get my water.)"

    "(As I approached the water fountain Bodhi called me two more times, and by the time I got a drank and sat down, he called be three more times.)"

    "(I finally accepted the sixth call.)"

    lead "Where were you? I called you many times to no response."

    fly "..."

    lead "I see ok, next time please update us in chat that you are not at your desk, it is not hard to write 'I am not at my desk' in chat I hope?"

    fly "..."

    lead "Sounds good, did you finish up the documentation task?"

    fly "..."

    lead "ok forget the documentation task I am writing a different ticket for you right now, there was a person who would facilitate the process of doing a release for our application and he got fired so now you will do it yourself I will tell you when I am done writing it."

    fly "..."

    lead "Ok, sounds good. Thank you."

    fly "..."

    jump Day_4_Illiterate

label Day_4_Illiterate:

    scene bg blackscreen

    "(Did I have lunch?)"

    "(Did I have my sugar water?)"

    "(What happened in the last hour?)"

    boss "Hey did you get to read and start the ticket we talked about?"

    "(His sudden appearance made me jump.)"

    fly "..."

    boss "Oh, it seems like you don't look so well."

    fly "..."

    boss "I'm sorry to hear that, look you don't have to disclose anything about your condition to me, it is actually preferable that you do not. Take a bit to rest, but if I can ask, did you at least get the chance to read the ticket?"

    fly "..."

    boss "What, do you just lack the ability to read or something? It's just words, read them. Then let me know, Thank you."

    "(I went back to my tickets, and clicked the ticket Drucker assigned me.)"

    "(When it finished loading, I realized that it was completely incomprehensible.)"

    "(I no longer was able to read anything on the page.)"

    "(I needed to get out of my desk, take a walk, anything, but as I got up out of my desk Bodhi called me.)"

    lead "Hello good afternoon. Did you finish the documentation task I asked about?"

    fly "..."

    lead "Oh you do not look well, you should take a break. but that documentation task is very important, please get it done by today. I will let you know when the ticket I mentioned is finished."

    lead "Sounds good, thank you."

    "(I got out of my chair again, I stood there for a couple of seconds awaiting something to interupt me but thankfully nothing did. I then rushed to the nearest empty quiet room.)"

    jump Day_4_End_of_Day

label Day_4_End_of_Day:


    "(I sat in the quiet room alone and stared at myself in the mirror.)"

    "(Why am I here?)"

    "(When did I take this job?)"

    "(When did I start working?)"

    "(How long have I been working?)"

    "(What am I working for?)"

    "(Where am I?)"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Oh pathetic insect who tangled himself in the spiders web.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Oh pathetic insect who flew straight into the spiders abode.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Did you expect to have a dialogue with the spider?{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Did you expect to get sympathy from the spider?{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Or perhaps, do you feel obligated to sustain the spider?{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Oh poor pathetic insect.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}You have fallen into the arms of what will not benefit you.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Oh poor pathetic insect.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}The spider is quickly approaching, ready to rip you apart limb by limb.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Oh poor pathetic insect.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}There is a way out if you try, there is a way out if you struggle, there is a way out even if it hurts.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Oh poor pathetic insect.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Do you forsake what is difficult for what is easy?{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Then my dear pathetic insect{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Close your eyes, relax and let yourself go.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Let your legs go.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Let your wings go.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Let your face go.{/color}"

    "{color=#7E6D87}Let your eyes go.{/color}"

    "(I left the room and went back to my desk, the time I spent alone in the quiet room did not help me relax my mind, it only caused it to rot further.)"

    "(When I went back to my desk I was immediately interrupted by Drucker.)"

    boss "Hello hello, if you don't get to it today it is fine, but did you get the chance to read the ticket?"

    "(Right after that Bodhi began calling me.)"

    fly "..."

    boss "Who cares about the call what I am asking is more important."

    fly "..."

    boss "Based off you're response, you did not. Alright I guess, maybe you should just take the day off, a bit disappointing though."

    "(After he left, I attempted to pick up the call from Bodhi but it cut out before I could accept.)"

    fly "..."

    "(I waited for a few minutes anxiously wondering if he was going to call again. Was there an internet problem? Did he change his mind? Did someone else interupt him? Was he stabbed in the back from an unknown assassin?)"

    fly "..."

    "(20 minutes had passed and nothing.)"

    fly "..."

    "(I looked at the clock and it was 4:50PM, time had left without me.)"

    fly "..."

    "(I began packing, but just before I turned off my laptop, I got the call.)"

    lead "Hello, were you able to get the documentation done?"

    fly "..."

    lead "I see, no worries you can get to it tomorrow. I also finished writing the other ticket I mentioned, please get both done tomorrow. Have a good night."

    "(And the call ended.)"

    fly "..."

    jump Final_Act_Day_5_At_Home
